data.name: AlertBox5.Text
data.value: Some applications & control Panel applets use "MS Shell Dlg" font. There is a registry trick that substitutes these fonts by other fonts. They are originally substituted by "Microsoft Sans Serif" and "Tahoma".

data.name: AlertBox7.Text
data.value: To return to default in Windows 7 & 8.1: press on undo buttons below and logoff and re-logon your Windows, then return to WinPaletter and reload "Default Windows" from the button above, apply and logoff
